description: The world of health care can be so confusing. It's hard to figure out what's going on when people use jargon words like, "deductible," "co-pay," and "co-insurance." Let Health Care Genius give you a hand. Just ask!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Health Care Genius, "What's a deductible?"
Alexa, tell Health Care Genius to define, "co-pay."
Alexa, ask Health Care Genius for the definition of co-insurance.
name: Health Care Genius
shortDescription: Health Care Genius can help you understand strange terms in health care. For example, you can ask, "What's a deductible?"
